    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been absolutely wonderful to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my daily commutes. There are a few tiny signs of love here and there, but honestly, it still looks great and drives like a dream! I\u2019ve taken really good care of it, and I\u2019d love to see it go to a great new home. Feel free to shoot me a message if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
