    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a driver-spec 2005 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and an 8,000 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec M-Variable limited-slip differential. Mechanical highlights include a documented VANOS system overhaul and proactive rear subframe reinforcement to maintain torsional rigidity. The suspension has been refreshed with polyurethane bushings for sharper turn-in response. While showing honest signs of use, the powertrain remains robust, delivering the visceral, analog feedback this chassis is celebrated for.",
      "price": 34500.0,
