      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously cared for and remains in impressive condition. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, with only minor stone chips on the front fascia that are barely noticeable from a distance. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free environment featuring supple leather seats with minimal wear and perfectly functioning climate and infotainment systems. Mechanically, it is robust; the engine pulls smoothly through every gear, and a full service history confirms it has never missed a scheduled maintenance interval. The tires have ample tread remaining, and the brakes feel firm and responsive. It\u2019s a turnkey example ready for its next owner to enjoy immediately.",
