    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that\u2019s as reliable as it is fun to drive? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape, runs like a dream, and has been super well-maintained over the years. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a road trip, this beauty is ready to go. Come take it for a spin\u2014I think you\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 34500.0,
